{
  "title": "Garlicky Kissed German Chervil Toast",
  "description": "A simple, pillowy German dish featuring chervil, perfect for a lazy Sunday morning. This recipe is macrobiotic-friendly, making it a great option for those following a balanced diet.",
  "cuisine": "german",
  "diet": [
    "macrobiotic",
